{"tid":2512902,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"點睇日日屈人五毛pr果班人開始學人講「邏輯」","createTime":"2021-05-02T06:01:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-02T06:14:13.000Z","uid":123264,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"809a14c8cf7aba96aa01a669fed3476883eee337","tid":2512902,"uid":123264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T06:01:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />講邏輯 我同你講囉<br />\n咁所以講左咁耐屈五毛屈pr既証據呢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無証據就可以隨便屈人 咁照計我屈番你pr都得?<br />\n連仔之前捉左幾個pr帳號 呢單野只係証明實際上係有pr存在 完全唔係某d會員可以拎黎打飛機既「証據」<br />\n根本本質就同小粉紅無分別 非我族類就係五毛<br />\n不過佢地屌你果陣就用「賣國美分」字眼 而呢班人就用「pr五毛」字眼<br />\n個邏輯係邊?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0081bd0ae3f7daf91b5f93ff961ed151cc231330","tid":2512902,"uid":59976,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T06:03:29.000Z","msg":"所以連囝應該要整返個演算法，咁連登先會和平<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fb3f7008a302002dd471f1e3aded32c6602c6ac","tid":2512902,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T06:14:13.000Z","msg":"連登最撚明顯個PR就係LIKIN<br />\n但就無人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}